plot: Khloé is forced to examine her insecurities when she receives constant criticism about her weight gain from the media--and from family members. Can she learn to love herself and not worry about making everyone else happy? She also gets fed up with constantly cleaning up after her filthy hubby Lamar, so she decides to give him a yucky taste of his own foul medicine. But it's game on when Lamar refuses to give in and Khloé refuses to back down.—Guilherme O.
